<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head><meta charset="UTF-8" /><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" /><title>Otelturizm · Rezervasyon Güncellendi</title></head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#F3F1ED;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Inter,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;color:#1A1919;">
  <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%" style="background:#F3F1ED;padding:36px 12px;"><tr><td align="center">
    <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="620" style="max-width:620px;background:#fff;border-radius:22px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 14px 38px rgba(15,23,42,.12);">
      <tr><td style="background:#E30A17;padding:30px;color:#fff;text-align:center;"><div style="font-size:13px;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:800;">Rezervasyon Merkezi</div><div style="margin-top:9px;font-size:23px;font-weight:900;">Rezervasyonun güncellendi</div></td></tr>
      <tr><td style="padding:28px;">
        <p style="margin:0 0 12px;font-size:18px;">Merhaba <strong>{{user_first_name}}</strong>,</p>
        <p style="margin:0 0 18px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;color:#334155;"><strong>{{hotel_name}}</strong> için <strong>#{{booking_reference}}</strong> numaralı rezervasyon tarihlerin güncellendi. Güncel fiyat oda takvimine göre yeniden hesaplandı.</p>
        <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:0 10px;">
          <tr><td style="padding:14px;border:1px solid #EBE9E4;border-radius:14px;background:#F8FAFC;"><strong>Eski rezervasyon</strong><br/>{{old_check_in_date}} → {{old_check_out_date}} · ₺{{old_total_price}}</td></tr>
          <tr><td style="padding:14px;border:1px solid #BFDBFE;border-radius:14px;background:#EFF6FF;"><strong>Yeni rezervasyon</strong><br/>{{check_in_date}} → {{check_out_date}} · {{night_count}} gece · ₺{{total_price}}</td></tr>
          <tr><td style="padding:14px;border:1px solid #EBE9E4;border-radius:14px;background:#F8FAFC;"><strong>Oda</strong><br/>{{room_type_name}} · Ortalama gecelik ₺{{nightly_price}}</td></tr>
        </table>
        <p style="margin:18px 0 0;font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;color:#6E6E77;">Otel, güncellenen tarihleri panelinde görecek ve gerekli onay adımlarını tamamlayacaktır.</p>
      </td></tr>
      <tr><td style="padding:18px 22px;background:#FCFBF9;border-top:1px solid #EBE9E4;color:#6E6E77;text-align:center;font-size:12px;">© 2026 Otelturizm · Rezervasyon No: #{{booking_reference}}</td></tr>
    </table>
  </td></tr></table>
</body>
</html>
